---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Own Your Mind — independent, practitioner-led coverage of decentralised AI."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'About' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        <strong>Own Your Mind</strong> is an independent, practitioner-led content platform covering decentralised AI.
      </p>

      <p>
        Our editorial position is simple: <strong>Freedom AND returns. Sovereignty-first. Hands-on.</strong>
      </p>

      <p>
        We believe the next generation of AI infrastructure will be decentralised — owned by participants rather than
        corporations. We write about it from the perspective of someone actually running the nodes, staking the tokens,
        and building on the protocols.
      </p>

      <h2>What we cover</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Why DeAI</strong> — The thesis for decentralised AI and why it matters</li>
        <li><strong>Projects</strong> — Honest reviews with freedom scores, not sponsored content</li>
        <li><strong>Tokenomics</strong> — How the tokens actually work, from a practitioner view</li>
        <li><strong>Build</strong> — Hands-on tutorials for running your own infrastructure</li>
        <li><strong>Journal</strong> — Weekly dispatches from the frontier</li>
        <li><strong>Resources</strong> — Directories, reference material, and tools</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who</h2>

      <p>
        Built by <a href="https://x.com/0xBobski" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@0xBobski</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>

      <p>
        Reach out on <a href="https://x.com/ownyourmindai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X (@ownyourmindai)</a> or <a href="https://x.com/0xBobski" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@0xBobski</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
